comment: Faried (DEN) makes contact with Ellis' (IND) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.

Gallinari (DEN) legally contests Ellis's (IND) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five' contact after the release of the shot is considered incidental.
